snippet.title: Venkaiah Naidu Alleges Opposition of Changing Stand over Note Ban Issue

localized.description:
Winter Session of Parliament 2016: Union Minister Venkaiah Naidu alleges opposition of changing stand over note ban issue. Opposition parties are attacking PM Modi for demonetising Rs 500 and Rs 1000 notes without any preparation.
